| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2816 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5ac6ee7b-9243-52db-9996-d115c5b312ce"
